Definition: any of various small animals or insects that are pests
Example: e.g. cockroaches or rats; cereals must be protected from mice and other vermin; he examined the child's head for vermin; boys in the village have probably been shooting vermin
Synonyms: adj, all, offensive, verminous, pest, any, of, various, small, animals, or, insects, that, are, pests, e, g, cockroaches, rats, cereals, must, be, protected, from, mice, and, other, he, examined, the, child, s, head, for, boys, in, village, have, probably, been, shooting
Category: noun.animal
